title: Mark Normand Returns! Private Jet Trash
description:
Kippy and Foley are back with comedian and podcast host Mark Normand! Mark joins the guys for a few beers and answers fan questions! Its a hot one! You know Mark Normand from Tuesday's with Stories and Joe Rogan Podcast!


Bonus Episodes: www.Patreon.com/AreYouGarbage 


Shirts: www.PodcastMerch.com 


Follow Kevin: https://www.instagram.com/kevinryanco... Follow Foley: https://www.instagram.com/foleygrams/ Comedians H. Foley and Kevin Ryan are self proclaimed GARBAGE. Each week a new stand up comedian gets put to the test. Steal shampoo from hotels? Own a George Foreman Grill? Ever worn JNCO Jeans?
